        <h4>Innovation Leadership</h4>
        <p>SRS pioneered DSP in lock-in amplifiers, direct digital synthesis in function generators, and rational approximation synthesis in RF generators — earning multiple R&amp;D Innovation Awards.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="fact">
        <h4>Employee Owned</h4>
        <p>Over 90% of shares are held by current employees, ensuring quality and customer trust come before short-term financial pressures.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="fact">
        <h4>Space Qualified</h4>
        <p>Our RGA100 mass spectrometer was adapted for NASA and operates on the International Space Station for continuous ammonia leak detection.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="fact">
